description:
The Chase UK: Celebrity Special

Season 2, Episode 2

Bradley Walsh presents as comedian Jimmy Carr, Coronation Street's Jack P Shepherd (David Platt), retired rugby union player Matt Dawson and Commons Speaker's wife Sally Bercow pit their wits against ruthless quiz genius the Chaser in the hope of winning thousands of pounds for charity. They must work as a team to answer general knowledge questions against the clock and race down the game board to the exit without being caught
